parameters.text:
=I have received an email. Please use your "google_sheets" tool to find the relevant information about my services or pricing if the sender is asking about them. Then, generate a reply based ONLY on that data.

SENDER INFO:
From: {{ $json.from?.value?.[0]?.address || "Unknown" }}
Subject: {{ $json.subject || "No Subject" }}
Message Content: {{ $json.text || $json.html || "" }}

Requirement: Return the response in the required JSON format only.

parameters.jsCode:
const rawData = $input.first().json.output; 

let parsedData;

try {
  parsedData = typeof rawData   === 'string' ?  JSON.parse(rawData) : rawData;
} catch (e) {
  parsedData = rawData;
}

return {
  email_subject: parsedData.subject,
  email_body: parsedData.body
};
